<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <% include ./partials/head.ejs %>
    </head>
    <body id="home">

        <!-- Navigation -->
        <% include ./partials/navbar.ejs %>

        <!-- Jumbotron Header -->
        <% include ../static/partials/messages.ejs %>
        <header id="mainJumbo" class="jumbotron">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                        <% if(currentUser){ %>
                            <h1 class="display-3">Hello <%= currentUser.username %>!</p>
                            <% if(currentUser.role === 0) { %>
                                <p class="lead">Want to be able to create private wikis? Click below to upgrade your account!</p>
                                <form action="users/<%= currentUser.id %>/upgrade" method="POST">
                                    <script
                                        src="https://checkout.stripe.com/checkout.js" class="stripe-button"
                                        data-key="pk_test_SzCvbipJ9yfY4isz80dsfHoV"
                                        data-amount="1500"
                                        data-name="Blocipedia"
                                        data-description="Upgrade Account to Premium"
                                        data-image="https://stripe.com/img/documentation/checkout/marketplace.png"
                                        data-locale="auto">
                                    </script>
                                </form>
                            <% } else if(currentUser.role === 1) { %>
                                <p class="lead">Click below to downgrade your account from premiun to standard</p>
                                <a href="/users/<%= currentUser.id %>/downgrade" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Downgrade</a>
                            <% } %>
                        <% } else if(!currentUser) { %>
                            <h1 class="display-3">Drop your knowledge</p>
                            <p class="lead">This is Knowledge Drop, the premier knowledge hub of the web. Come join a large open-source community dedicated towards the transfer of information. From apples to Zoroastrianism, you can share your knowledge on any topic with the rest of the world or learn about topics that you never even knew existed!</p>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                    <% if(!currentUser) { %>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                            <form id="signup-form" method="POST" action="/users/signup">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="title">Username</label>
                                    <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="Pick a username" class="form-control"/>
                                    <small class="text-muted" id="titleHelp">username must be 4 or more characters in length and not being used.</small>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com" class="form-control"/>
                                    <small class="text-muted" id="titleHelp">email must be valid.</small>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="password">Password</label>
                                    <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Create a password" class="form-control"/>
                                    <small class="text-muted" id="passwordHelp">password must be 6 or more characters in length.</small>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="password_conf">Password Confirmation</label>
                                    <input type="password" name="password_conf" placeholder="Re-enter your password" class="form-control"/>
                                    <small class="text-muted" id="password_confHelp">enter the password again.</small>
                                </div>
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Sign up for Knowledge Drop</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="jumbotron feature">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 d-none d-lg-block">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="https://cdn0.iconfinder.com/data/icons/users-android-l-lollipop-icon-pack/24/student-512.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                        <h5 class="display-4">Learn</h5>
                        <p class="lead">With users from around the world sharing their knowledge, there is no limit to what you can learn. From Aa to Zoology, you are free to learn what you want, when you want. It is only a click away.</p>
                        <a href="/wikis" class="btn btn-primary">Start Exploring</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="jumbotron feature">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <% if(!currentUser) { %>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                            <h5 class="display-4">Connect</h5>
                            <p class="lead">A premier source for user-generated content. Connect, share, and learn about any topic. If you don't find it, add it and share your knowledge with the world.</p>
                            <a href="/users/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Join Today</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 d-none d-lg-block">
                            <img class="img-fluid float-right" src="https://cdn1.iconfinder.com/data/icons/material-core/20/language-512.png">
                        </div>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                            <h5 class="display-4">Share</h5>
                            <p class="lead">Share your knowledge with the community by creating your own Wiki. Have full control over how your wiki looks by using markdown syntax.</p>
                            <a href="/wikis/new" class="btn btn-primary">Create A Wiki</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 d-none d-lg-block">
                            <img class="img-fluid float-right" src="https://cdn3.iconfinder.com/data/icons/glypho-free/64/share-512.png">
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="jumbotron feature">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 d-none d-lg-block">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="https://cdn3.iconfinder.com/data/icons/knowledge-management-glyph-2/64/collaborative-combine-hand-together-team-512.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                        <h5 class="display-4">Collaborate</h5>
                        <p class="lead">Work with other members from around the world to have the most complete Wiki possible. We allow you to edit and have control over content as a Wiki Admin.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Premium Content</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="jumbotron feature">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                        <h5 class="display-4">Protect</h5>
                        <p class="lead">Premium Users have access to private wikis that only they can see. You can choose who you would like to share with and who can contribute content as a Premium User.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 d-none d-lg-block">
                        <img class="img-fluid float-right" src="https://cdn0.iconfinder.com/data/icons/very-basic-android-l-lollipop-icon-pack/24/lock-512.png">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- <% include ./partials/footer.ejs %> -->

        <% include ./partials/baseScripts.ejs %>
    </body>
</html>